   <h1><fieldset>Chapter 8: User Options</fieldset></h1>
   <p>
   This chapter explains the different options of HDFView
   accessible from the Tools menu.</p>
   
   <ul class="ul">
   <li><a href="ug08useroptions.html#ug08general">8.1 General Settings</a></li>
       <ul class="ul">
       <li><a href="ug08useroptions.html#ug08directory">8.1.1 Working Directory</a></li>
       <li><a href="ug08useroptions.html#ug08help">8.1.2 User's Guide Path</a></li>
       <li><a href="ug08useroptions.html#ug08fileaccess">8.1.3 File Access Mode</a></li>
       <li><a href="ug08useroptions.html#ug08extension">8.1.4 File Extensions</a></li>
       <li><a href="ug08useroptions.html#ug08libversion">8.1.5 Library Versions</a></li>
       <li><a href="ug08useroptions.html#ug08font">8.1.6 Text Font</a></li>
       <li><a href="ug08useroptions.html#ug08imageopt">8.1.7 Image Options</a></li>
       <li><a href="ug08useroptions.html#ug08dataopt">8.1.8 Data Options</a></li>
       <li><a href="ug08useroptions.html#ug08objectcount">8.1.9 Number of Open Objects</a></li>
       <li><a href="ug08useroptions.html#ug08displayind">8.1.10 Display Indexing</a></li>
       </ul>
